  "title": "Engineer (Private Residential Condominium Projects)",
  "description": "<h2>Engineer (Private Residential Condominium Projects)</h2>\n<p>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</p>\n<h2><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preparing and manage overall master schedule integrating work breakdown structure</li>\n  <li>Preparing schedule bar chart plan considering all in puts (manpower, equipment and materials) availability, production and construction sequences</li>\n  <li>Developing and update resources (manpower, equipment's and materials) availability, production and construction sequences</li>\n  <li>Inspect and monitor daily the work happening on site</li>\n  <li>Participate all meeting (ie. Schedule review meeting, progress meeting, coordination meeting, constructability review meeting and so on)</li>\n  <li>Record / Document weekly progress meeting held with the client, consultants and sub-contractors</li>\n  <li>Liaising with managers and engineers to discuss the progress of the project and address any issues that arise</li>\n  <li>Developing contract and construction programmes and construction project plans</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Engineering and/or relevant field</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years’ of local experience in private residential and condominium projects</li>\n  <li>Well-versed in sequence of works and authority requirement</li>\n  <li>Proficient in planning works and material schedules</li>\n  <li>Familiar with Ms Project is preferred</li>\n</ul>",
